Kale Group, a Turkish ceramics
maker, bought the entire stake of Industrie Fincuoghi SpA, an
Italian maker of wall and floor tiles, for an undisclosed price, 
Hurriyet  reported, citing Kale chairwoman Zeynep Bodur Okyay.  To contact the reporter on this story:
